'''玛恩村屠杀'''是[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]期间发生于2014年2月9日的一起屠杀事件。这起屠杀针对的是居住在玛恩村（Maan）的阿拉维派村民。

2014年2月9日，来自“叙利亚伊斯兰阵线”旗下的“[[阿克薩戰士|阿克薩戰士]]”（Jund al-Aqsa）组织的反对派武装袭击并占领了[[哈马省|哈马省]]的[[阿拉维派|阿拉维派]]村庄玛恩。在占领玛恩村期间，据叙利亚人权观察组织（SOHR）报道反对派武装杀害了21名平民，<ref name=voiceofrussia>{{Cite web |url=http://voiceofrussia.com/news/2014_02_10/Rebels-kill-21-civilians-in-Syria-Alawite-village-NGO-7356/ |title=Rebels kill 21 civilians in Syria Alawite village - NGO |accessdate=2014-04-23 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025150543/http://voiceofrussia.com/news/2014_02_10/Rebels-kill-21-civilians-in-Syria-Alawite-village-NGO-7356/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=bbc>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-26114068 |title=More Syrians flee besieged Homs Old City |accessdate=2014-04-23 |archive-date=2018-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181220042055/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-26114068 |dead-url=no }}</ref>其中14人是妇女。<ref name=naharnet>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/119092-syria-army-seizes-alawite-massacre-village |title=Syria Army Seizes Alawite 'Massacre' Village |accessdate=2014-04-23 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019131919/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/119092-syria-army-seizes-alawite-massacre-village |dead-url=no }}</ref>被害人中有10人来自同一个家庭。在进攻中还有20名亲政府的民兵被杀。<ref name=voiceofrussia/><ref name=bbc/>叙利亚国家媒体声称反对派的这一袭击是一场屠杀，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/syria-600-evacuated-blockaded-homs-22432511 |title=Rebel Attack on Syrian Alawite Village Kills 40 |accessdate=2014-04-23 |archive-date=2014-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140224000142/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/syria-600-evacuated-blockaded-homs-22432511 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而叙利亚政府的消息称在屠杀中有60名平民被[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]]背景的“叙利亚伊斯兰阵线”成员杀害，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://breakingnews.sy/ar/article/33688.html |title=Ban Ki-moon condemns the Maan massacre |access-date=2014-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025152128/http://breakingnews.sy/ar/article/33688.html |archive-date=2014-10-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="TurkeyAlawite">[http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2014/02/turkey-alawite-identity-syria-arab-war.html Syria war sparks Turkish Alawite anxiety] {{Wayback|url=http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2014/02/turkey-alawite-identity-syria-arab-war.html |date=20171011182244 }} [[Al_Monitor|Al Monitor]], 19 February 2014</ref>其中大部分是妇女、儿童和老人。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/syrian-peace-talks-resume-acrimoniously-as-assad-regime-alleges-hama-massacre/2014/02/10/c571aa84-927c-11e3-b3f7-f5107432ca45_story.html |title=Syrian peace talks resume acrimoniously as Assad regime alleges massacre in Hama |accessdate=2014-04-23 |archive-date=2017-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171011015245/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/syrian-peace-talks-resume-acrimoniously-as-assad-regime-alleges-hama-massacre/2014/02/10/c571aa84-927c-11e3-b3f7-f5107432ca45_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

反对派组织“[[努斯拉陣線|胜利阵线]]”否认他们参与了袭击，声称是另一组织进行了这一袭击。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2014/2/10/un-brokered-syriatalksresumeingeneva.html |title=Syria peace talks resume; warring parties still far from agreement |accessdate=2014-04-23 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025150546/http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2014/2/10/un-brokered-syriatalksresumeingeneva.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>联合国秘书长[[潘基文|潘基文]]的发言人转达了潘基文对这一事件表达的“巨大震惊”。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.un.org/News/Press/docs//2014/sgsm15639.doc.htm |title=Secretary-General |accessdate=2014-04-23 |archive-date=2014-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140217171727/http://www.un.org/News/Press/docs/2014/sgsm15639.doc.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

这一事件引起了土耳其[[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]、[[梅尔辛省|梅尔辛省]]、[[哈塔伊省|哈塔伊省]]及其他地区阿拉维派社区针对[[基地组织|基地组织]]、胜利阵线、土耳其[[正义与发展党|正义与发展党]]以及美国的抗议示威活动。<ref name="TurkeyAlawite"/>

